    "#2.3. Ventas y conversiones\n",

    "first_purchase = orders.groupby('Uid')['Buy Ts'].min().reset_index()\n",

    "\n",
    "#2.5. Marketing: CAC y ROMI\n",
    "\n",
    "users_by_source = visits.groupby('Source Id')['Uid'].nunique()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Gastos por fuente\n",
    "costs_by_source = costs.groupby('source_id')['costs'].sum()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Costo de adquisici√≥n por cliente (CAC)\n",
    "cac = (costs_by_source / users_by_source).dropna()\n",
    "print(\"CAC por fuente:\\n\", cac)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ingresos por fuente\n",
    "orders_with_source = orders.merge(visits[['Uid','Source Id']], on='Uid')\n",
    "revenue_by_source = orders_with_source.groupby('Source Id')['Revenue'].sum()\n",
    "\n",
    "# ROMI = (Ingresos - Costos) / Costos\n",
    "romi = (revenue_by_source - costs_by_source) / costs_by_source\n",
    "print(\"ROMI por fuente:\\n\", romi)"
